title: HTC One A9 price, specifications leak ahead of October 20 launch: here’s everything we know so far
text: HTC One A9 price, specifications leak ahead of October 20 launch: here’s everything we know so far Friday, 16 October 2015 (10 minutes ago) HTC is gearing up for its October 20 event where the company is expected to finally unveil the One A9, its first smartphone that runs on Android 6.0 Marshmallow out-of-the-box. With less than a week to the expected launch, the leaks have far from stopped and it has now been spotted on French carrier Orange website. Here’s everything we know about the forthcoming smartphone so far. HTC One A9 design: From the numerous leaked photos we have come across so far, HTC seems to have opted for a very iPhone-like design. The front is dominated by the display with thick bezels and a home button at the bottom. At the back is a protruding camera with an LED flash placed at the center.
